In[6]:
def categorize_age(age):
    if age>60:
        return 'Above 60'
    elif 20 <= age <= 60:
        return '20 to 60'
    else:
        return 'Below 20'
df['Age Group']= df['Age'].apply(categorize_age)
print(df)
